Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.78,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você se sente sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:32.57,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você consegue me ouvir agora?
