Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:02:00.22,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}E eu estou chamando o seu nome de novo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.48,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Se você estiver se apegando ao medo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.65,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Se eu soubesse que os olhos podem se abrir
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.44,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Que a luz passe por aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.82,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}E eu pergunto:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:18.41,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Por que não podemos parar com todos estes sacrifícios?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:24.00,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Eu sei que todas as mentiras viraram pedra no seu coração
